nt states, beyond which laminarisation is certain, confirms the hole\nformation scenario and shows that it is more pronounced in larger systems.\nFinally, the examination of non reactive trajectories, where a hole opens then\ncloses, indicates that hole opening and closing are distinct processes. Both\nthe vortices and the streaks reform concomitantly when the laminar holes close.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 16:08:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 30 Jul 2021 20:03:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-29"}
