y in this doping type converted (NA > ND)\nGa2O3 material is of significance and impact for the design of Ga2O3 power\nelectronics devices.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 19:23:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-28"}
