linking\ncon-straints. In summary, the adequate choice of aggregation methods strongly\ndepends on the mathematical structure of the considered energy system\noptimization model, and a priori decisions of a sufficient temporal aggregation\nare only possible with good knowledge of this mathematical structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 20:05:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Apr 2021 07:15:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-02"}
