. The results\nsuggest that there were both children who benefitted from the characters in\nthis task and those who performed better without them. The factors that\ndifferentiated these two categories are currently unclear. To help further\nresearch on phonetic mnemonics in literacy learning software, we are making the\ncharacters available to the research community.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Mar 2021 22:16:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-01"}
