st section discusses the\nopen questions related with each topic, which can be considered by the\nsimulations and the future spacecraft mission. We close by summarizing the\nfuture BepiColombo opportunities, which is a joint mission between ESA and\nJAXA, and is en route to Mercury.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 31 Mar 2021 02:48:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 17:52:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 11 Aug 2021 14:40:11 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 14:33:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-07"}
